rriman served as chief executive officer of royal appliancedirt devil inc a  million public company from august  to april  he led a turnaround of the company through accelerated new product development global sourcing and an aggressive marketing strategy since leaving royal appliancedirt devil inc merriman joined american greetings a  billion consumer products company which specializes in greeting cards and other online social expressions as the chief financial officer in september  he joined the board of american greetings in  and served until the company went private in august  he rejoined the board of the private company in january  from november  until november  merriman served as the president and chief executive officer of the lamson  sessions co a  million manufacturer of plastic conduit fittings switch and outlet boxes sold primarily to home depot lowes and electrical distributors until the successful sale of the company to thomas  betts corporation merriman is currently an operating advisor for resilience capital partners llc a private equity firm focused on principal investing in lower middle market underperforming and turnaround situations invacare corporation nyse ivc headquartered in elyria ohio is a global leader in the manufacture and distribution of innovative home and longterm care medical products that promote recovery and active lifestyles the company has  associates and markets its products in  countries around the world for more information about the company and its products visit invacare’s website at wwwinvacarecom   take your pick buyouts delivers exclusive news and analysis about private equity deals fundraising topquartile managers and more get your free trial or subscribe now vc journal provides exclusive news and analysis about venture capital deals fundraising topquartile investors and more get your free trial or subscribe now sign up to our newsletter receive updates from our pe hub wire and top stories of the week newsletters first nam